source.name: Characteristics of New Housing
source.description: Provides national, annual data on the characteristics of new privately-owned residential structures, such as square footage, number of bedrooms and bathrooms, type of wall material, and sales prices. Many characteristics are available at the region level. Data are funded by HUD and are collected in the Survey of Construction (SOC).
